@page "/"

<div class="hero">
    <h1>Wolfs <span>Trucking Co</span></h1>
    <p>
        Full service trucking and 3PL warehouse company headquartered in Lenoir, North Carolina.
        Port drayage, local and regional delivery, and nationwide logistics through our brokerage network.
        From the mountains of western NC to every port and distribution center on the East Coast.
    </p>
    <a class="btn btn-primary" href="@RouteConstants.Login.TrimStart('/')">Get Started</a>
</div>

<div class="services-grid">
    <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">&#x1F69A;</div>
        <h3>Port Drayage</h3>
        <p>
            Container hauling from the ports of Charleston, Savannah, Norfolk, and Wilmington.
            Chassis management, container tracking, and guaranteed appointment windows.
            Licensed and bonded for all major East Coast port terminals.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">&#x1F4E6;</div>
        <h3>Local &amp; Regional Delivery</h3>
        <p>
            Same-day and next-day delivery across North Carolina, South Carolina, Virginia, Tennessee,
            and Georgia. Dedicated routes through Charlotte, Asheville, Greenville, and the Piedmont Triad.
            LTL and FTL options with liftgate and white glove service.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">&#x1F30E;</div>
        <h3>Nationwide Brokerage</h3>
        <p>
            Access to thousands of vetted carriers through our brokerage network for coast-to-coast freight.
            Real-time tracking, competitive spot and contract rates, and a dedicated account manager
            for every shipment from origin to destination.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">&#x1F3ED;</div>
        <h3>3PL Warehousing</h3>
        <p>
            Climate-controlled and dry storage at our Lenoir facility with pick-and-pack,
            cross-docking, inventory management, and order fulfillment.
            EDI integration and real-time inventory visibility through our driver portal.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">&#x1F4CB;</div>
        <h3>Fleet Management</h3>
        <p>
            GPS tracking on every truck, ELD compliance, automated HOS logging,
            DVIR electronic inspections, and IFTA fuel tax reporting.
            Dispatch optimization routes through our AI-powered scheduling engine.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">&#x1F4AC;</div>
        <h3>Voice Dispatch</h3>
        <p>
            Real-time voice communication between dispatch and drivers via our built-in
            MCP-powered voice chat. Route changes, delivery confirmations, and emergency
            alerts without taking hands off the wheel.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h2 class="card-title">Why Wolfs Trucking Co</h2>
    <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-value">24/7</div>
            <div class="card-label">Dispatch Available</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-value">98.6%</div>
            <div class="card-label">On-Time Delivery Rate</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-value">150+</div>
            <div class="card-label">Active Routes</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-value">NC DOT</div>
            <div class="card-label">Licensed &amp; Insured</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
